#   Executive Summary
Unity Bank Uganda has experienced increasing operational workloads across its retail banking operations. Senior management requires a centralized dashboard to monitor case volumes, analyst productivity, branch performance, SLA compliance, and operational efficiency. The objective of this project is to design a Business Intelligence dashboard that provides timely insights and supports data-driven operational decision-making.

## Business Questions
Our dashboard must answer these questions.

## Executive View
•	How many cases did we receive? 
•	How many have been completed? 
•	How many are still open? 
•	Are we meeting our SLA? 
•	Which branches are performing well?                                                             
•	Which branches need attention? 

## Analyst Performance
•	Which analyst closes the most cases? 
•	Which analyst has the longest turnaround time? 
•	Who has the biggest backlog? 

## Operations
•	Which products generate the most requests? 
•	Which case types take the longest? 
•	Which regions have the most workload? 
•	Are escalations increasing? 

## Customer
•	Which customer segment raises the most requests? 
•	Which requests are highest risk?

          
